'Apparently Freshpet food is the best food than ordinary dog food [sic],' he says. 'He wants to eat it every night, every day. Apparently now that's good food!'

At one point in the commercial, which appears to be largely unscripted, the little boy tells viewers to call him - before giving out his telephone number. 

'Just call the Apparently Kid when you see this commercial,' he says. 'Bye and apparently!'

Noah became an internet sensation after giving a hilarious interview with  WNEP at the Wayne County Fair in August and was later invited to appear on the Ellen DeGeneres Show.

